---

<section class="mb-8">
  <div class="effect-slide">
    <img
      src="/images/tokyotower.jpg"
      alt="Tokyo Tower"
      title="Tokyo Tower"
      loading="lazy"
    />
  </div>
  <div class="mb-6">
    <h1
      class="font-bold uppercase text-center text-4xl md:text-5xl xtracking-tighter py-6 overflow-hidden"
    >
      <span
        class="bg-gradient-to-br from-[#334155] via-[#1e293b] to-[#0f172a] dark:from-primary-main dark:via-primary-main dark:to-primary-main bg-clip-text text-transparent"
      >
        こんにちは!
      </span>
    </h1>
    <div
      class="border-b-[1px] border-t-[1px] border-current py-1 flex items-center justify-center gap-1"
    >
      <a
        class="unset ml-4 hover:text-text-link"
        href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/fabrizio-pace/"
        aria-label="Fabrizio on LindedIn"
        target="_blank"
      >
        <i
          class="fa-brands fa-linkedin"
          aria-hidden="true"
          title="Fabrizio on LindedIn"></i>
        <span>LinkedIn</span>
      </a>
      <a
        class="unset ml-4 hover:text-text-link"
        href="https://github.com/fabriziopace"
        aria-label="Fabrizio on GitHub"
        target="_blank"
      >
        <i
          class="fa-brands fa-github"
          aria-hidden="true"
          title="Fabrizio on GitHub"></i>
        <span>GitHub</span>
      </a>
      <a
        class="unset ml-4 hover:text-text-link"
        href="https://community.neptune-software.com/users/fabriziopace"
        aria-label="Fabrizio on Neptune Software Community"
        target="_blank"
      >
        <i
          class="fa-solid fa-neptune"
          aria-hidden="true"
          title="Fabrizio on Neptune Software Community"
        >
          <i
            class="fa-regular fa-neptune-content"
            aria-hidden="true"
            title="Fabrizio on Neptune Software Community"></i></i
        >
        <span>Neptune</span>
      </a>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div>
    <p class="mb-8">
      Hello! I am Fabrizio, a Full Stack Developer working at <a
        href={"https://jdtech.it"}
        aria-label="Jdtech Website"
        target="_blank">Jdtech</a
      >.
    </p>
    <p class="mb-8">
      Over the years I gained strong technical skills as well as excellent
      interpersonal skills, enabling me to interact with a wide range of people.
    </p>
    <p class="mb-8">
      More than 7 years of experience managing Neptune Software, SAP and
      JavaScript frameworks with aim to develop responsive and multi-platform
      apps.
    </p>
    <p class="mb-8">
      I love learning new technologies and sharing knowledge in the <a
        href={"https://community.neptune-software.com"}
        target="_blank"
        aria-label="Neptune Software Community">Neptune Software Community</a
      >.
    </p>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .effect-slide {
    position: relative;
    display: inline-block;
    overflow: hidden;
  }

  .effect-slide:before {
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
    content: "";
    position: absolute;
    bottom: 0;
    left: 0;
    mix-blend-mode: hue;
    background: black;
    animation: slide-right-left 2s linear 1 forwards;
  }

  @keyframes slide-right-left {
    0% {
      width: 100%;
    }
    100% {
      width: 0%;
    }
  }
</style>
